'''Under 23''' is a category of [[Athletics (sport)|athletics]] in which athletes compete under from 20 to 22&nbsp;years on 31 December of the year of the competition.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.european-athletics.org/files/regulations/2012/2012.05.21./400-European%20Athletics%20U23%20Championships%20Regulations-May2012.pdf|title=EUROPEAN ATHLETICS UNDER 23 CHAMPIONSHIPS|publisher=european-athletics.org|accessdate=31 January 2013}}</ref>
